Paralax Video Enterprises Inc said itsigned a definitive agreement to buy &lt;American Video Group Inc>for stock.    According to the merger proposal, American Videoshareholders will receive about 287,700 restricted Paralaxshares, and warrants to buy another 318,600 restricted sharesat six dlrs a share. The warrants run for three years.    In addition, it said holders of American Video convertibledebentures agreed to exchange their holdings for about 380,000dlrs worth of Paralax stock.    American Video operates stores in U.S. military bases. Reuter&#3;